Q: How to run the program?
A:
0. To create the executable, run "make".

1. At least 6 arguments are required:
./myrobot old_x old_y old_z new_x new_y new_z <-tv|-sv>

2. Example:
./myrobot 3 4 5 -1 -2 -3 -tv
or
./myrobot 3 4 5 -1 -2 -3

3. In the program: press 's' to side view, press 't' to top view, press 'v' to change view whatever.
Press 1 to select base to rotate, press 2 to select lower arm, press 3 to select upper arm.
